reviewText: Wow, this course was amazing and very interesting!
Отличный курс для изучения принципов функционального программирования на скале. Немного не хватает практики.
The course offers a good introduction to Scala and Functional Programming principles. I learned a lot, thanks!
The course gives a much deeper understanding than a basic course on Scala. It's from the Scala creator himself.Martin is the best
I think this course gives me a lot of help in FP.

Un curso muy bien estructurado e impartido.
